high_descs: Walk ahead and left to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the pot in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the shelves at the end of the corner on the right.
Place the pot on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pot on a shelf.

high_descs: Go forward and to the left to turn and face the stove.
Pick the pot up from the stove.
Go to the right and face the sink.
Put the pot in the sink and turn the water off and then on and then pick up the pot.
Turn around and cross the room and turn to the right and face the brown shelves.
Put the pot on the right side of the shelf second from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on a shelf.

high_descs: Walk forward to the stove top.
Pick up the large pot from the stove top.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the pot in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to the shelves on the right near the wall.
Put the pot on the right side of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned pot on a shelf.
